Shape.Name: Watchdog should not beactive during bootloader
Shape.Text: nan

Shape.Name: disable internal Watchdog
Shape.Text: nan

Shape.Name: Auto Wiping
Shape.Text: nan

Shape.Name: Use AUTOSAR standardized application interfaces and architecture
Shape.Text: The body controller SHALL integrate existing Exterior Light software components that are provided by the customer

Shape.Name: Integration of Exterior Light software components
Shape.Text: The body controller SHALL integrate existing Exterior Light software components that are provided by the customer

Shape.Name: Speed detection
Shape.Text: If higher speed is detected without detecting more rain the wiper rate must be increased

Shape.Name: Higher speed and more rain detection
Shape.Text: If higher speed an more rain is detected the wiper rate must be increased

Shape.Name: Integration of Exterior Light software components
Shape.Text: The Wiper Washer software component SHALL provide AUTOSAR interfaces as defined in the AUTOSAR Specification 'AUTOSAR_ApplicationInterfaces_Explanation_BodyComfort.pdf' (Revision 3.2.1)

Shape.Name: Use AUTOSAR standardized application interfaces and architecture
Shape.Text: The Wiper Washer software component MUST provide AUTOSAR interfaces as defined in the AUTOSAR Specification 'AUTOSAR_ApplicationInterfaces_Explanation_BodyComfort.pdf' (Revision 3.2.1)

Shape.Name: Rain detection
Shape.Text: If more rain is detected the wiper rate must be increased

Shape.Name: Front wiper disabled if engine hood is opened
Shape.Text: The wiper washer controller SHALL disable the front wiper immediately if EngineHoodState <> CLOSED

Shape.Name: Front wiper disabled if driver door is opened
Shape.Text: The wiper washer controller SHALL disable the front wiper immediately if DriverDoorState <> CLOSED

Shape.Name: Front wiper diabled if passenger door is opened
Shape.Text: The wiper washer controller SHALL disable the front wiper immediatley if PassengerDoorState <> CLOSED

Shape.Name: Front washer disabled if front wiper disabled
Shape.Text: The wiper washer controller SHALL disable the front washer immediately if the the front wiper is disabled

Shape.Name: Faster wiping if car speed is higher
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the wiper washer controller SHALL increase the speed of the wiper depending on the VehicleLongitudinalSpeed

Shape.Name: Higher sensitifity when it is dark
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the wiper washer controller SHALL increase the speed of the wiper depending on the OutsideBrigness data provided by the Exterior Light software component.

Shape.Name: Faster wiping if car speed is higher
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the speed of the wiper SHALL increase if the speed of the car increases

Shape.Name: Faster wiping if amount of rain is higher
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the wiper washer controller SHALL increase the speed of the wiper depending on the value of the amount of rain measured by the rain sensor connected to the ECU

Shape.Name: Front washer disabled if sun roof is opened
Shape.Text: The wiper washer controller SHALL disable the front waher if SlidingRoofState <> CLOSED

Shape.Name: Front wiper disabled if engine hood is opened
Shape.Text: The front wiper SHALL be disabled if the engine hood is opened

Shape.Name: Front wiper disabled if front door is opened
Shape.Text: The front wiper SHALL be disabled if a front door is opened

Shape.Name: Faster wiping if amount of rain is higher
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the speed of the wiper SHALL increase if the amoint of rain increases

Shape.Name: Front washer disabled if front wiper disabled
Shape.Text: The front washer SHALL be disabled if the front wiper is disabled

Shape.Name: Auto Wiping on user request
Shape.Text: The wiper washer controller SHALL enable auto wiping if HMIActivateAutoWiping is set to 'on'.

Shape.Name: Configurable sensitifity of auto wiping
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the wiper washer controller SHALL configure the sensitifity of the auto wiping algorithm based on HMIIntervalWipingSpeed

Shape.Name: Auto Wiping on user request
Shape.Text: The driver SHALL have the possibility to enable or disable auto wiping

Shape.Name: Configurable sensitifity of auto wiping
Shape.Text: The driver SAHLL have the possibility to configure the sensitifity of the auto wiping function

Shape.Text: Increasing of the wiper rate must be linked to the user configuration

Shape.Name: Frequence of Wiper
Shape.Text: Frequence of Wiper must be linked to user configuration

Shape.Name: Auto Wiping
Shape.Text: The front wiper SHALL support auto wiping

Shape.Name: Disable WiperWasher
Shape.Text: Automatically disable Wiper Washer

Shape.Name: Reset
Shape.Text: Reset of Controller after WD Time

Shape.Name: Restart
Shape.Text: Restart Controller after not possible Reset

Shape.Name: Front washer disabled if sun roof is opened
Shape.Text: The front waher SHALL be disabled if the sun roof is opened

Shape.Name: Turn-Off
Shape.Text: User must be able to turn off Wiper completely

Shape.Name: Sensor sensivity brightness
Shape.Text: Sensor sensivity must be increades by lower outside brightness

Shape.Name: Higher sensitifity when it is dark
Shape.Text: If auto wiping is enabled the sensitifity SHALL increase if the outside brightness decreases
